text: Branimals () is a 2009 Brazilian animated movie. It is directed by Paulo Munhoz. It stars Marino Junior, Mário Schoemberger, Renet Lyon, Fabíula Nascimento and Michelle Pucci. == Other websites == * * Category:2009 movies Category:2009 animated movies Category:2009 adventure movies Category:Brazilian movies Category:Movies about animals
